    Aware, BeanClassLoaderAware, BeanFactoryAware, DisposableBean, FactoryBean<ClientResources>, InitializingBean

    public class ClientResourcesFactoryBean
extends AbstractFactoryBean<ClientResources>
    FactoryBean that creates a ClientResources instance representing the infrastructure resources (thread pools) for a Redis Client.
